headline: Carrier Named a 2025 Organization of the Year for Excellence in Customer Service
summary: Carrier Global Corporation (NYSE: CARR), global leader in intelligent climate and energy solutions, has been named an Organization of the Year in the 2025 Excellence in Customer Service Awards by the Business Intelligence Group. The annual awards recognize companies transforming customer service through innovation, responsiveness and tangible impact.
